*Smijem* da ti pomognem? (Can I help you?)

On *smije* da ide sa nama. (He is allowed to come with us.)

*Smijala* se cijelu veče. (She was laughing all night.)

*Smijeh* se širio u sobi. (Laughter was spreading in the room.)

*Smiješno* je sve što se desilo. (Everything that happened is funny.)

*Smiješ* mi se. (You are smiling at me.)